  "name": "vyges/tlul-apb-adapter",
  "version": "0.1.0",
  "description": "A generic TileLink Uncached Lightweight (TL-UL) slave to AMBA APB master protocol adapter. Enables any APB-interfaced peripheral to be connected to a TL-UL crossbar without modification to either side. Supports APB3 and APB4 (PSTRB, PPROT, PSLVERR) via parameterization. Single-outstanding transaction model with zero-latency overhead and minimal gate count.",
  "license": "Apache-2.0",
